snippet.title: Ten Bells [WISHLIST TEASER] **PC Horror Game**
snippet.description:
Wishlist TEN BELLS on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3044030/Ten_Bells/
Wishlist LONG GONE on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1977610/Long_Gone/
Join the Discord: https://discord.com/invite/MJw3n2tHjt
Join the Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/HillfortGames 

TEN BELLS, Out August 2024!

You're trapped in an old English pub. Unravel a chilling tale by discovering anomalies while trying to escape. Confront the horror as you survive Ten Bell's endless loop.
